# Notary Coach AI – Subscription App

This project is a **paywalled AI coaching platform** designed for Notary Signing Agents (NSAs).  
It allows users to register, subscribe via **Stripe Checkout**, and then access an **AI assistant** (powered by OpenAI) that provides step-by-step guidance for loan signings, borrower communication, and business building.

## ✨ Features
- 🔑 **Secure authentication** with JWT
- 💳 **Stripe subscription paywall** (monthly recurring)
- 🤖 **OpenAI-powered Q&A** with an NSA-focused system prompt
- 🌐 **Frontend static site** with sign-in, subscribe, dashboard, FAQ, and checklist
- 📦 **FastAPI backend** for authentication, billing, and AI chat
- 🗄️ **SQLite database** (upgradeable to Postgres in production)

## 🧰 Tech Stack
- **Backend:** FastAPI, SQLAlchemy, Uvicorn
- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- **Payments:** Stripe Checkout + Webhooks
- **AI:** OpenAI Responses API (`gpt-5.1-mini`)
- **Auth:** JWT-based login & signup
- **Hosting:** Render (or any platform supporting Python & static sites)

---

⚠️ **Disclaimer:** This tool is for educational and business coaching purposes only. It is **not legal advice**.  
Users should always follow their state’s SOS, title/escrow, and underwriter requirements.
